<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Work+Sans:400,600" rel="stylesheet"> 

<div class="rbodyp">
<h1>Songs</h1>

<p>Here you can find tons of indepedant US artists from all over the country. Each state has his own local artists. Discover new horizons through different states : from Florida to Winsconsin</p>

<table class="table table-hover table-striped table-dark">
  <thead>
    <tr >
        <th>Title</th>
        <th>Desc</th>
        <th>Genre</th>
        <th>Artist</th>
        <th>Year</th>
        <th colspan="3"></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @songs.each do |song| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= song.title %></td>
        <td><%= song.desc %></td>
        <td><%= song.genre %></td>
        <td><%= song.artist %></td>
        <td><%= song.year %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Show', song, :class => "btn btn-info" %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_song_path(song) %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', song,:class => "btn btn-danger", method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<br>
<%= link_to 'New Song', new_song_path, :class => "btn btn-outline-warning" %>  

</div>